{"tid":1524540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講咗咁奈 黑警點還眼？","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:11.000Z","uid":211369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1002e0c913bc6c10ec56b8b6d34cfd94d7cb3f97","tid":1524540,"uid":211369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:53.000Z","msg":"相信大家經過今日31/8都好火<br />\n除咗21/7翻版之外仲有第四位眼受傷嘅手足<br />\n冇錯係第四隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話還眼咁狗仔可以點還？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以我所知男性人體一共有四隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左右馬屎</span><br />\n如果有啲狗仔唔好彩嘅話...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警還眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本故事內容純屬虛構 如有雷同 實屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fcaeaec9de2047be0e92d28aee26139d3af854","tid":1524540,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9月1, 1300機場<br />\n你知點做未? 未知就睇啦</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">自由服飾, 唔洗黑衫, 唔入T1T2, 帶埋個GIP, 免口號, 免傳單</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(有禁制令,藐視法庭會入獄)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsAjL4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsAjL4W.jpg&h=f128e56d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a5d35a2591528d7fe2e0a1dae43b79354ca0cf0","tid":1524540,"uid":211369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"